Regression example

Simple text

This is a simple, bivariate regression example. Two plus two equals 4.

2 + 2
## [1] 4

Tidy some data

Here we tidy the data. Este codigo sirve para manipular el tamao del grafico. Me puede servir para los graficos del QP.

my_data <- spanish %>%
  select(., x = X14461gll, y = X14473gll) %>%
  filter(., y < 0.06, x < 0.075)

my_data %>%
  ggplot(., aes(x = x, y = y)) +
  geom_point() + 
  geom_smooth(method = 'lm')

Model

Here we fit a model.

my_fit <- lm(y ~ x, data = my_data)

my new model

data1 <- spanish %>%
  select(., x = X14466gll, y = X14459gll)

data1 %>%
  ggplot(., aes(x = x, y = y)) +
  geom_point() + 
  geom_smooth(method = 'lm')

# fit
fit1 <- lm(y ~ x, data = data1)
summary(fit1)
